# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NEXUS STOCK AI — Environment Variables
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env to git — it contains secrets.
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Supabase (Persistent NGX Price Storage) ──────────────────────
# Get these from: https://app.supabase.com → Project Settings → API
# Required for real data accumulation and AI self-improvement.
# Without these, the server works but all data resets on each restart.
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here

# ── Server Port ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Render sets this automatically — only override for local development.
# PORT=5002
